title: ‘The Challenge: Spies, Lies, and Allies’ Episode 2 | Death, Taxes, and Bananas
description:
Johnny Bananas is joined by The Ringer’s Juliet Litman to discuss all the drama and strategy from Episode 2 of ‘The Challenge.’ They discuss the emerging vets vs. rookies dynamic (9:30), who is building the best strategy so far this season (15:30), the love triangle from hell between Nelson, Ashley, and Berna (40:30), their love for new arrival Ed (48:00), and so much more.
Host: Johnny Bananas
Guest: Juliet Litman
Associate Producer: Sasha Ashall
